import math
from bisect import bisect_right

def find_gcd_in_range(a, b, queries):
    gcd = math.gcd(a, b)
    factors = []
    i = 2
    while i * i <= gcd:
        if gcd % i == 0:
            factors.append(i)
            if i * i != gcd:
                factors.append(gcd // i)
        i += 1
    factors.sort()
    results = []
    for (low, high) in queries:
        ans = -1
        index = bisect_right(factors, high)
        if index > 0 and factors[index - 1] >= low:
            ans = factors[index - 1]
        results.append(ans)
    return results
